{"tid":2499590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港交通資訊網：九巴車長間流傳消息肇事車長昨日接種第二劑科興疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-22T04:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T06:20:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"34f2a2091d8173f3db34d63e41f8eb4a8d131fc0","tid":2499590,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/146006188753214/posts/4067974916556302/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F146006188753214%2Fposts%2F4067974916556302%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=33fef335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/146006188753214/posts/4067974916556302/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n今早九龍城碼頭總站九巴鏟上花槽意外中，肇事巴士在意外發生約三小時後由九巴拖車拖回路面。九巴車長間流傳消息指肇事車長曾於昨日接種第二劑科興疫苗，今早意外時因頭暈而發生意外，但有關消息尚未獲得證實，確實原因有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTWhZSKP4u6RJaNSJBANVZBiuTzA1Y2J9w3vgvfDYE9gM?filename=jt2MmRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjt2MmRM.jpg&h=5ef23a07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a52874880945db07f16135090dfda5bf95de74d","tid":2499590,"uid":17443,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"血栓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b036d7e639f20894b7a3f499ebc48a411c6eeb","tid":2499590,"uid":56230,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩總站開出<br />\n真係見頭暈咪撚開啦"},{"pid":"dbae64469290d12419faad506866654324a1fcc9","tid":2499590,"uid":35930,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"打科興打到要踎監 呢鋪都算係代表作"},{"pid":"09fc32f0f780abac1f6bd2ec5301d25ba522dcc8","tid":2499590,"uid":45123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"接種科興會變公路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/mou